<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
body { font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #334155; background: #f8fafc; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; }
.card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
.brand { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: #6366f1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 8px; }
p  { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.amount { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #6366f1; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center; }
.detail { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
.detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
.detail-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 8px; margin-top: 8px; }
.footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 32px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="brand">GROVA Work</div>
    <h1>Factura {{ mes }}</h1>
    <p>Hola, adjunto encontrarás la factura correspondiente al período <strong>{{ mes }}</strong>.</p>

    <div class="amount">€{{ invoice.totalFloat|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</div>

    <div class="detail">
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Salario base</span>
            <span>€{{ invoice.salarioBaseFloat|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if invoice.diasBonus > 0 %}
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Bonus ({{ invoice.diasBonus }} día(s))</span>
            <span>€{{ invoice.montoBonusFloat|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% for line in invoice.bonusLines %}
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span>{{ line.concepto ?: ('work.invoice_email_manual_bonus'|trans({}, 'work')) }}</span>
            <span>€{{ line.importeFloat|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span>Total</span>
            <span>€{{ invoice.totalFloat|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>Se adjunta el PDF con el detalle completo de días trabajados y datos bancarios para la transferencia.</p>

    <div class="footer">GROVA Work Module · Generado automáticamente</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
